  <name>OpenAudioTools</name>
  <summary>Real-time voice analysis and feminization training tool</summary>

  <description>
    <p>
      OpenAudioTools is a comprehensive voice analysis platform designed to help users understand
      and modify their vocal characteristics through objective, real-time feedback.
      While useful for any vocal analysis, the app is specifically optimized for voice feminization.
    </p>
    <p>Key features include:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Real-time spectrograms and target zones for vocal training.</li>
      <li>Advanced resonance tracking via F1 and F2 formant analysis.</li>
      <li>Detailed metrics for pitch, jitter, shimmer, and prosody.</li>
      <li>Objective feedback loops to assist in gender-affirming voice transitions.</li>
    </ul>
  </description>

  <launchable type="desktop-id">com.ktvincco.openaudiotools.desktop</launchable>

